descriptionHtml:
Winterhold
once one of the most powerful and mighty cities in all Tamriel
and capital of magic

history claims that Winterhold was once a large part of Skyrims glory though fate took a turn for the worst and plunged it to the sea of ghosts
now its true glory still shines through rubble of mighty temples and palaces of the once great city
includes:
palace (could use some work)
college (now better and shining with personality
docks (complete with wharfs docks and cargo)
wall ( ruined but still standing)
markets (no shop keepers but still a sight)
stables (no stable men :/ )
houses (doubled and fit for a city)
mountain shrine (by far my favourite part :) )
